room_title: Escape room "The Jewel Thief" by Keynundrum in Topeka
room_address: 2900 SW Atwood, Suite C Topeka, KS 66614
room_description: The famous Faith Diamond has been stolen and you are pretty sure you know who took it. Sneak into his office and poke through his things to find proof of the heist. Can you crack the safe and escape the room before he returns?
